40|$|Communication has {{revolutionized}} by the Satellites. Its {{importance and}} services to human race cannot be neglected. In general, it helps us to predict weather, storm warning and also provides communication services in many fields like telephone, mobiles, television etc. In <b>satellites</b> <b>Communication</b> between two parties {{can be done by}} various modulation techniques. For example: FDMA, TDMA, CDMA. This paper describes the history of satellite communications, its types and its technological trends in different areas especially mobile communications...|$|R
